__data__.response:
Humans do not currently live on any of these planets. Humans are native to the planet Earth.

Mars is a rocky planet in our solar system that has been explored by several robotic spacecraft, but it does not have an atmosphere suitable for human habitation.

Venus is also a rocky planet with a thick atmosphere, but its surface temperature is extremely hot and hostile to humans.

Earth is the only known planet in the universe where humans can live.
